in the deli.

269
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:25,240
Well, at least he's got
a free garage.

270
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,840
Right, no good to him.

271
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,560
His Hillman
smells all fishy.

272
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:30,000
