for the sodding tiger.

302
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:22,280
No, no, no,
where's Michael Ellis now?

303
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,840
Oh, I don't know.

304
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,240
He said
it wasn't important, anyway.

305
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:27,040
All right,
here I come.

306
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:41,560
<i>[♪]</i>

307
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:45,200
<i>Hello, and welcome</i>
