00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:30,720
End of the announcement.

325
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:34,800
And now,
back to<i> University of the Air</i>

326
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:37,200
and our series for
advanced medical students,

327
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:40,360
<i>Elements of Surgical</i>
<i>Homeopathic Practice.</i>

328
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,800
Part 68, "Ants."

329
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,840
Oh, we're in luck again,
Marcus.

330
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:50,920
Hello, formicidophiles.

331
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:52,640
Well, before all the
blood and guts

332
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:54,160
you're waiting to see,

333
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:57,000
